quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  19,12,(Umuhungu we yarabwiwe ati) “Yewe Yahaya! Akira iki gitabo (Tawurati) ugikomereho. Kandi twamuhaye ubushishozi akiri muto.”
  19,13,"Ndetse twanamuhaye igikundiro ari impuhwe ziduturutseho, tunamweza ibyaha kandi yubahaga Allah"
  19,14,Ndetse yumviraga ababyeyi be kandi ntiyari intakoreka cyangwa ngo yigomeke (kuri Allah ndetse no ku babyeyi be)
  19,15,"Amahoro nabe kuri we umunsi yavukiyeho, umunsi yapfiriyeho ndetse n’umunsi azazurirwaho"
  19,16,"Babwire inkuru ya Mariyamu mu gitabo (cya Qur’an, yewe Muhamadi), ubwo yitaruraga umuryango we akajya ahagana iburasirazuba"
  19,17,"Maze agashyira urusika hagati ye na bo, nuko tumwoherereza Roho wacu (Malayika Gaburiheli) amwiyereka mu ishusho ry’umugabo uteye neza"
  19,18,"(Mariyamu) aravuga ati “Mu by’ukuri niragije Nyagasani Nyirimpuhwe ngo andinde ikibi cyaguturukaho, niba koko utinya Imana (ntunyegere).”"
  19,19,(Malayika) aravuga ati “Mu by’ukuri ndi intumwa ya Nyagasani wawe ije kuguha (inkuru) y’impano y’umuhungu wejejwe (ibyaha).”
  19,20,"(Mariyamu) aravuga ati “Ni gute nagira umuhungu kandi nta mugabo nigeze, ndetse nkaba ntarigeze niyandarika?”"
  19,21,"(Malayika) aramubwira ati “Uko ni ko bizagenda! Nyagasani wawe aravuze ati “Ibyo kuri njye biroroshye. (Turashaka) kumugira ikimenyetso ku bantu (kigaragaza ubushobozi bwacu) n’impuhwe ziduturutseho, kandi iryo ni iteka ryamaze gucibwa.”"
  19,22,"Nuko (Mariyamu) aramutwita (Issa), maze amwitarurana kure (y’abantu)"
  19,23,"Nuko ibise bimujyana ku ruti rw’umutende, aravuga ati “Mbega ububabare! Iyo nza kuba narapfuye mbere y’ibi, nkanibagirana burundu.”"
  19,24,Nuko yumva ijwi munsi ye rimuhamagara rigira riti “Ntugire agahinda! Rwose Nyagasani wawe yashyize isoko y’amazi munsi yawe.”
  19,25,"Unanyeganyeze uruti rw’umutende, rurakumanurira itende nziza kandi zihishije"